WEBVTT

00:04.101 --> 00:06.402
Morning.
Morning.

00:06.404 --> 00:09.155
You, by chance, have the number
of a good chiropractor?

00:09.157 --> 00:10.423
What about Alan?

00:10.425 --> 00:14.660
