on Valentine's Day.

05:14.634 --> 05:18.753
Uh, how much
is your Presidential Suite?

05:20.305 --> 05:21.806
Uh-huh, I-I see.

05:21.808 --> 05:23.507
Um, do you, by any chance,

05:23.509 --> 05:26.043
