Secretary of Agriculture Suite?

05:29.064 --> 05:31.348
All right, all right,
you know what, let me just book

05:31.350 --> 05:33.484
your best regular-people room,
and, uh,

05:33.486 --> 05:37.238
would it be possible to, uh,
split the deposit

05:37.240 --> 05:40.557
over three credit cards?

05:40.559 --> 05:42.576
Oh, oh, sure, I'll hold.

05:43.912 --> 05:45.913
Oh, oh, hey,
how'd it go with Kate?

05:45.915 --> 05:49.316
Let's just say she doesn't
want me in her business.

05:49.318 --> 05:51.702
Financial or lady.

05:51.704 --> 05:53.254
Oh, oh, I'm sorry.

05:53.256 --> 05:55.189
Yeah, the only reason
she wanted to see me

05:55.191 --> 05:58.092
was to give me this stupid check
for $100,000.

06:02.297 --> 06:05.433
(softly):
You're not stupid to me.

06:07.135 --> 06:08.469
So, uh, what's
the next step?

06:08.471 --> 06:09.937
There is no next step.

06:09.939 --> 06:12.056
It's over.
What are you talking about?

06:12.058 --> 06:14.275
She doesn't want anything
to do with me.

06:14.277 --> 06:15.309
(scoffs)

06:15.311 --> 06:16.444
Well, there's a good attitude.

06:16.446 --> 06:18.062
Let me ask you something.

06:18.064 --> 06:20.314
Was it over for Lyndsey and me

06:20.316 --> 06:22.432
when I burned her house
to the ground?

06:23.602 --> 06:24.601
No.

06:24.603 --> 06:25.870
Was it over for us

06:25.872 --> 06:27.822
when I introduced
her mom to my mom,

06:27.824 --> 06:30.124
who subsequently turned her
into a rapacious lesbian? No.

06:30.126 --> 06:33.127
And-and-and what about
me living in this house?

06:33.129 --> 06:35.496
Was it over when my brother died
and you bought the place?

06:35.498 --> 06:36.797
Sadly, no.

06:36.799 --> 06:39.500
Right, because I am not
a quitter.

06:39.502 --> 06:41.068
And you aren't, either.

06:41.070 --> 06:44.255
You're Walden Schmidt,
captain of industry.

06:44.257 --> 06:46.390
Titan of technology.

06:46.392 --> 06:48.476
Head honcho of...

06:49.811 --> 06:51.679
...handsomeness.

06:51.681 --> 06:52.930
Ran out of steam?

06:52.932 --> 06:56.233
Yes, but you'll notice
I did not quit.

06:57.068 --> 06:58.402
Maybe you're right.

06:58.404 --> 06:59.603
Of course I'm right.

06:59.605 --> 07:02.139
Nothing is over until
you say it's over.

07:02.141 --> 07:04.124
With the possible exception
of me moving out,

07:04.126 --> 07:05.809
which will only happen
when you wheel me

07:05.811 --> 07:07.244
into the assisted
living facility.

07:07.246 --> 07:08.445
You're right.

07:08.447 --> 07:09.780
I'm going to go
talk to her.

07:09.782 --> 07:10.748
Thank you, Alan.

07:10.750 --> 07:12.066
No problem, buddy.

07:12.068 --> 07:14.651
I will always be here for you.

07:15.670 --> 07:17.204
Literally.

07:18.540 --> 07:20.975
Oh, uh, hello.

07:20.977 --> 07:22.176
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.

07:22.178 --> 07:24.828
Um, I have a MasterCard,

07:24.830 --> 07:27.715
