and my mom's Visa.

07:34.055 --> 07:35.806
Walden.

07:35.808 --> 07:37.007
Great, you've already showered.

07:37.009 --> 07:38.559
Now, get dressed.
We're going to dinner.

07:38.561 --> 07:40.144
