but here I am.

08:00.082 --> 08:02.199
I am not going to dinner
with you.

08:02.201 --> 08:04.218
Fine.

08:04.220 --> 08:06.754
You don't want to go to dinner
with me, then...

08:07.756 --> 08:10.925
...then we will have
dinner right here.

08:10.927 --> 08:13.894
Look, your favorite:
a half-eaten lobster

08:13.896 --> 08:15.229
with a
cigarette butt in it.

08:15.231 --> 08:18.098
