for coleslaw

08:18.100 --> 08:20.234
with a Band-Aid in it.

08:22.737 --> 08:24.822
Come on, Kate,
go to dinner with him.

08:24.824 --> 08:27.408
Don't be so shellfish.

08:27.410 --> 08:28.609
(laughing)

08:28.611 --> 08:30.611
You know you're an idiot, right?

08:30.613 --> 08:32.413
I'm a persistent idiot.

08:32.414 --> 08:33.496
(sighs)

08:33.499 --> 08:34.898
Let me get dressed.

08:37.118 --> 08:38.402
Yay.

08:44.626 --> 08:46.961
Why would I do that?

08:49.681 --> 08:52.683
Oh, hey, there's
my valentine.

08:52.685 --> 08:54.351
Will you be mine?

08:54.353 --> 08:56.253
Hi, Alan.
Yes, I will.

08:56.255 --> 08:57.771
Great, 'cause I got something
special planned.

08:57.773 --> 08:59.273
Is this going to be
another scavenger hunt

08:59.275 --> 09:00.691
