14:47.163 --> 14:49.029
(laughs)

14:49.031 --> 14:50.865
I really missed you.

14:50.867 --> 14:52.116
Me, too.

14:52.118 --> 14:55.152
Can I tell you a secret, though?
Sure.

14:55.154 --> 14:58.372
Sam Wilson is a much
better lover than you.

15:00.425 --> 15:01.926
I'm sorry.

15:01.928 --> 15:05.045
