15:22.648 --> 15:24.281
<i>Marie Claire.</i>

15:24.283 --> 15:26.350
Doesn't look
much like a heart.

15:26.352 --> 15:28.536
Well, it's bleeding like one.

15:29.371 --> 15:30.454
