15:30.456 --> 15:31.455
Oh...

15:31.457 --> 15:32.706
Oh. Oh, my God.

15:32.708 --> 15:33.690
This is the end.

15:33.692 --> 15:34.691
I'm seeing lights.

15:34.693 --> 15:36.243
You're not dying.

15:36.245 --> 15:37.328
