pulled over.

15:37.330 --> 15:39.213
Oh, nice job, lead foot.

15:40.916 --> 15:42.366
Do you want to keep
your other ball?

15:43.752 --> 15:44.718
Evening, ma'am.

15:44.720 --> 15:46.036
Do you know why I
pulled you over?

15:46.038 --> 15:47.304
I know I was speeding,

15:47.306 --> 15:48.538
but I have a very good excuse.

15:48.540 --> 15:49.557
Is that so?

15:49.559 --> 15:50.591
Show him, Alan.

15:50.593 --> 15:51.708
What? No!

15:51.710 --> 15:52.726
Show him.

15:52.728 --> 15:54.228
Oh...

15:54.230 --> 15:56.931
Oh, sweet mother of God!

15:58.650 --> 16:00.067
Is that a heart?

16:02.487 --> 16:05.222
Thank you.

16:07.192 --> 16:08.576
(gasps)
Oh, my God!

16:08.578 --> 16:10.527
Wha...? Alan, no.

16:14.399 --> 16:15.950
Sorry. What's...
what's going on?

16:15.952 --> 16:17.234
