to believe this.

16:17.236 --> 16:20.120
My business partner
just found a factory.

16:20.122 --> 16:22.623
We can start production
on my line immediately.

16:22.625 --> 16:23.874
That's great.

16:23.876 --> 16:25.259
Congratulations.

16:25.261 --> 16:27.544
Oh, my God, this
