16:27.546 --> 16:30.014
We leave for
China tomorrow.

16:30.016 --> 16:31.748
Tomorrow?

16:32.434 --> 16:35.102
Oh, you know what?
Wait...

16:35.104 --> 16:37.688
I'm gonna be in Japan

16:37.690 --> 16:39.807
