16:39.809 --> 16:41.225
I could hop over to China.

16:41.227 --> 16:42.726
We could get some
kung pao chicken,

16:42.728 --> 16:44.228
maybe adopt a baby.

16:45.063 --> 16:46.196
Oh...

16:46.198 --> 16:48.315
Kung pao chicken
is such a commitment.

16:49.818 --> 16:51.118
Ah, wait.

16:51.120 --> 16:53.170
In two weeks,
I have to be back here.

16:53.172 --> 16:54.705
Okay.

16:54.707 --> 16:56.373
Oh, how about
