convention with nerdier guys.

17:05.750 --> 17:07.334
You would be their queen.

17:07.336 --> 17:08.785
(laughs)

17:08.787 --> 17:11.422
Ah, no, that
won't work.

17:11.424 --> 17:12.423
Um...

17:12.425 --> 17:13.973
How about first week in May?

17:13.976 --> 17:15.559
I can do the second.

17:15.560 --> 17:17.560
And I can't.

17:19.564 --> 17:22.016
This was a lot easier
when we were both broke.

17:22.018 --> 17:24.018
