(chuckles)

17:24.853 --> 17:26.270
How about this?

17:26.271 --> 17:29.523
Are you free for sex
in 30 seconds?

17:29.525 --> 17:31.742
I have an opening.

17:33.111 --> 17:35.412
Let me check.

17:35.414 --> 17:37.331
Well, I'll
have to move

17:37.333 --> 17:39.166
