17:39.168 --> 17:40.334
(laughs)

17:44.706 --> 17:45.756
Hi.

17:45.758 --> 17:47.374
Hi.

17:47.376 --> 17:48.375
How you doing?

17:48.377 --> 17:50.127
I'm high,

17:50.129 --> 17:51.962
