17:53.214 --> 17:55.849
I'm sorry I ruined
Valentine's Day.

17:55.851 --> 17:57.051
What are you
talking about?

17:57.053 --> 17:59.669
Well, I wanted it to be special
because, you know,

17:59.671 --> 18:02.222
I haven't always been
the best boyfriend,

18:02.224 --> 18:06.226
